summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 41 of the Official Land Use Map (Volume 6 of Plats, page 20, Records of King County) to rezone property located at 8016 Ashworth Avenue North from Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) to Lowrise 1 (L 1) Multifamily Residential and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Pryde Johnson Ashworth, L.L.C., C.F. 306618, Project Number 2307253.)
